      <interpParagraph label="1003-2-g-Interp-2" marker="2.">
        <title>Adjustment of exemption threshold for banks, savings associations, and credit unions.</title>
        <content>For data collection in 2017, the asset-size exemption threshold is $44 million. Banks, savings associations, and credit unions with assets at or below $44 million as of December 31, 2016, are exempt from collecting data for 2017.</content>
